message:
Added initially support to handle Client-Organizations

With that, the API-Developer can control himself which organizations can
consume his API.

Documentation for the MainClass - Config instead of Contract

Added a diagram to illustrate and document the main classes of the program to help other to contribute.
Adn started to rename API-Contract with API-Config.
Now using API-Management 7.6.2 SP2 for Integration-Tests

Preparing rlease 1.3

Changed some of the log messages, better support for Windows, specific ErrorCode for a Breaking-Change
Small changes, added examples and documentation.
Added a note for SOAP-Service support. Still Beta

Prepare for release 1.5.0 

Added release notes and a deep link on how to contribute.
Bumping version number to 1.5.1 and added a few very small changes.
Improved log message and prepare for next release.
